Hi All,

Scheduling the meetup for Friday(24th June 2022) instead of a Thursday. Trying something new to get more traction on the attendance, please feel free to DM for any suggestions regarding the meetup schedule, presenting a topic or any other feedback.

The venue has been updated for this event, looking forward to seeing you all this Friday.

Please reach out if you have any questions.

Note: Developer Meetups is a “birds of feather” style informal meetups between community members with only developer-oriented technical content. Sales pitches, marketing presence, or recruiting are heavily frowned upon.

Regards,
